Package: ats-proxy-plugin
Version: 3.0-beta-1
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ats-core (>= 9.2.13), libssl3
Maintainer: ATS Proxy Enterprise <proxy@tripersonale.org>
Homepage: https://github.com/tripersonale/ats-proxy-enterprise
Description: ATS Proxy Enterprise v3.0 URL filtering and auth plugin
 Plugin with 5 modes (off, deny, whitelist, auth_all, auth_nd),
 salted SHA-256 password storage, IPv6 support.
 Includes ats-ctl CLI for policy management and ats-mode-test.sh.
